title: 18 — Pushable Objects
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify PushableTrait — pushing a heavy crate

---

# Go to the server room where the crate is
> east
[OK: contains "Server Room"]

# Examine the crate
> examine crate
[OK: contains "crate"]

# Try to take the crate (it's scenery — should fail)
> take crate
[OK: contains_any "can't" "fixed" "attached" "budge" "heavy"]

# Push the crate
> push crate
[OK: contains_any "push" "nudge" "budge" "effort" "move"]
